18
00:02:19,875 --> 00:02:22,845
Come on out, or you'll be sorry!

19
00:02:26,615 --> 00:02:29,445
<i>Vegeta was burning with rage after Gohan</i>

20
00:02:29,485 --> 00:02:31,845
