<i>Si Xing Qiu Ball from him.</i>

21
00:02:31,885 --> 00:02:37,255
<i>However, by then, Bulma and the</i>
<i>others had moved their hiding place.</i>

22
00:02:37,295 --> 00:02:41,585
<i>Further, in order to have</i>
<i>Gohan's dormant power drawn out,</i>

23
00:02:41,625 --> 00:02:47,365
<i>he was headed to the Grand</i>
<i>Elder's place, along with Kuririn.</i>

24
00:02:49,535 --> 00:02:55,635
<i>"Watch Out, Bulma!!</i>
<i>Si Xing Qiu Falls into Freeza's Clutches."</i>

25
00:03:40,925 --> 00:03:43,395
