29
00:04:09,655 --> 00:04:12,985
Where is the Dragon Ball?!

30
00:04:16,495 --> 00:04:18,285
There.

31
00:04:18,325 --> 00:04:21,265
Where is it?!

32
00:04:23,935 --> 00:04:28,565
I-I told you... it's right there.

33
00:04:28,605 --> 00:04:32,335
If you won't tell me,
then I'll just have to do this!

34
00:04:33,275 --> 00:04:37,675
<i>What are you talking about?</i>
<i>I've been telling you, haven't I?</i>

35
00:04:39,245 --> 00:04:42,545
