36
00:04:42,585 --> 00:04:45,315
It's there, I tell you!

37
00:04:49,855 --> 00:04:51,845
It was a dream, huh?

38
00:05:17,855 --> 00:05:20,155
<i>Damn it...</i>

39
00:05:21,185 --> 00:05:23,455
<i>If the device that kid was holding</i>

40
00:05:23,495 --> 00:05:27,855
<i>really is something that</i>
<i>can seek out Dragon Balls,</i>

41
00:05:27,895 --> 00:05:31,855
<i>then I can't be careless about leaving here.</i>

42
00:05:31,895 --> 00:05:34,865
<i>They wanted these six, too.</i>

43
00:05:34,905 --> 00:05:37,705
<i>All I can do is wait for</i>
<i>them to make their move.</i>

44
00:06:05,535 --> 00:06:08,495
<i>Freeza is starting to get pretty impatient, huh?</i>

45
00:06:08,535 --> 00:06:13,765
<i>That means I've destroyed the</i>
<i>spaceship's power, and he can't move.</i>

46
00:06:41,905 --> 00:06:46,195
<i>Even assuming that he radioed</i>
<i>to have more Scouters brought here,</i>

47
00:06:46,235 --> 00:06:48,865
<i>it would take three or four</i>
<i>days for them to get here, at best.</i>

48
00:06:48,905 --> 00:06:51,835
<i>I'll have to settle this before that time.</i>

49
00:06:51,875 --> 00:06:54,845
<i>If I can just acquire eternal</i>
<i>life with the Dragon Balls,</i>

50
00:06:54,885 --> 00:06:58,515
<i>then depending on my strategy,</i>
<i>I'm sure I will be able to defeat Freeza.</i>

51
00:06:58,555 --> 00:07:02,115
<i>Now, when he doesn't</i>
<i>have a Scouter, is my chance.</i>

52
00:07:19,575 --> 00:07:22,475
That miserable Vegeta!

53
00:07:46,935 --> 00:07:50,665
W-What is with all these earthquakes lately?

54
00:08:01,515 --> 00:08:06,645
That's it! I've had all I can
take of this crazy planet!

55
00:08:34,215 --> 00:08:39,515
Damn, it's going to take quite a bit
of time for us to get there at this speed.

56
00:08:39,555 --> 00:08:41,815
But if we use any more <i>ki</i> than this,

57
00:08:41,855 --> 00:08:45,515
that Vegeta bastard will
find us, no doubt about it.

58
00:08:45,555 --> 00:08:49,795
It looked like he had gotten even stronger.

59
00:08:49,835 --> 00:08:51,155
Right now, even with the two of us

60
00:08:51,195 --> 00:08:53,295
