there's no way we could beat him.

61
00:08:53,335 --> 00:09:00,065
But then, do I really have
enough power to rival Vegeta?

62
00:09:00,105 --> 00:09:02,165
I wouldn't think so.

63
00:09:02,205 --> 00:09:07,905
Well, I had <i>this</i> much latent power,
so with you having Saiyan blood,

64
00:09:07,945 --> 00:09:10,515
I think we're okay to expect quite a lot.

65
00:09:10,555 --> 00:09:12,455
Probably, anyway.

66
00:10:40,045 --> 00:10:42,835
It's not like I have to go in and get it, right?

67
00:10:42,875 --> 00:10:45,175
Even in the water like that,
it's still right nearby,

68
00:10:45,215 --> 00:10:46,845
the same as if it were on shore.

69
00:10:46,885 --> 00:10:50,815
Once Kuririn gets back,
I can just have him go get it.

70
00:10:50,855 --> 00:10:52,375
Sure.

71
00:11:17,875 --> 00:11:21,375
D-Don't tell me it's Vegeta!

72
00:11:24,215 --> 00:11:27,845
<i>What do I do? If Si Xing Qiu</i>
<i>falls into Vegeta's hands,</i>

73
00:11:27,885 --> 00:11:33,525
<i>he'll have all seven Dragon Balls,</i>
<i>and be granted eternal life.</i>

74
00:11:33,565 --> 00:11:36,695
<i>If that happens, then no matter</i>
<i>how much training Son-kun has done,</i>

75
00:11:36,735 --> 00:11:38,325
<i>he'll have no chance of winning.</i>

76
00:11:38,365 --> 00:11:39,825
<i>And that's not all.</i>

77
00:11:39,865 --> 00:11:43,495
<i>Yamucha and the others won't</i>
<i>be able to come back to life, either.</i>

78
00:11:43,535 --> 00:11:47,205
<i>And I'll never be able to return to Earth.</i>

79
00:11:47,245 --> 00:11:49,075
<i>All right...</i>

80
00:11:50,575 --> 00:11:53,915
Let's see, as I recall, it was this one.

81
